select count(1) from (
(select user_id from segment_profile where segment_id=6259 and version=20221221 and update_time=625920221221 )
except 
(select distinct a.union_id from dim_1 a 
join dim_1 b on a.union_id =b.union_id
join segment_profile c on b.pub_open_id = c.user_id 
where c.segment_id = 6259 and c.version = 20221221)
except 
(select distinct a.union_id from dim_2 a 
join dim_2 b on a.union_id =b.union_id
join segment_profile c on b.uid = c.user_id 
where c.segment_id = 6259 and c.version = 20221221)
)tt
LIMIT 0, 200
